All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
App
Main class of the application.
Board
Board is a class used to create and resize game field.
ChoiceController
ChoiceController is a class used to create and manage the second game window, where each player can select an army of his choice.
EndController
EndController is a class used to inform clients about endgame result.
Hexagon
Hexagon is a class used to fill and manage hexagonal battlefield of the game.
MainController
MainController is a class used to create and manage main game window, where the "battle" between clients begins and ends.
StartController
StartController is a class used to create and manage the very first game window, where each one of clients (players) can type username and connect to the server as well.
